obo:SYMP_0020043 obo:IAO_0000115 "A urinary system symptom that is characterized by an elevation in the concentration of the the pigments from foods, dyes, and medications in urine. The dilution of these pigment is dependent on the amount of water intake and severe dehydration can lead to a dark color." ;
    ns3:hasOBONamespace "symptoms" .

